Package com.tangosol.util

Class SafeSortedMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListMap<K,V>
com.tangosol.util.SafeSortedMap<K,V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, ConcurrentMap<K,V>, ConcurrentNavigableMap<K,V>, Map<K,V>, NavigableMap<K,V>, SortedMap<K,V>
public class SafeSortedMap<K,V> extends ConcurrentSkipListMap<K,V>
Implementation of a SortedMap extending ConcurrentSkipListMap to support null keys and null values. Note that unlike its super class, this class is not serializable.
Since:
23.03
Author:
mg
